			dat[x][i].b = (en[x][i] == MX) ? -1 : en[x][i] - i + 1;
			dat[x][i].id = i;
		}
		sort(dat[x], dat[x] + n);
	}
}

void build() {
	int i;

	for (N = 1; N < n; N *= 2);
	for (i = 0; i < N; i++) x[N + i] = -1;
	for (i = N - 1; i; i--) x[i] = max(x[i * 2], x[i * 2 + 1]);
	x[0] = max(x[1], x[2]);
}

void update(int i, int a) {
	i += N;
	x[i] = a;
	for (i /= 2; i; i /= 2) x[i] = max(x[i * 2], x[i * 2 + 1]);
	x[0] = max(x[1], x[2]);
}

